{"id": "1366466346887548988", "channel_id": "1366461968638017547", "type": 0, "author_id": "233903186048581632", "author_name": ".alice13th", "author_bot": false, "content": "I agreed, even English isn't my native language but translation right now is getting worse. I feel like it was done by lovecraftian weeb and made name cringier.", "timestamp": "2025-04-28T17:29:24.815000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366461968638017547", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Can we rollback the translations?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1366466722940326030", "channel_id": "1366461968638017547", "type": 0, "author_id": "633215996508766229", "author_name": "game.producer.light", "author_bot": false, "content": "I'm sorry, there might be some issues with the translation workflow. We are currently standardizing terminology, which may have caused changes to past terms and inadvertently overwritten some manual translations. At the same time, we have brought in a professional English translator to assist us, currently focusing primarily on the display of interface functions. She is also continuously monitoring everyone's feedback.\n\nWe hope to resolve combat-related texts within the next two months, followed by adjustments to the storyline. Right now is a somewhat chaotic transitional phase in the translation process, so we kindly ask for your patience. We hope to have the opportunity to share updates on the English localization progress with you later.\n\nPlease allow me to apologize for the unexpected negative language experience this may have caused!", "timestamp": "2025-04-28T17:30:54.473000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366461968638017547", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Can we rollback the translations?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
{"id": "1366476937244971008", "channel_id": "1366461968638017547", "type": 19, "author_id": "233903186048581632", "author_name": ".alice13th", "author_bot": false, "content": "Thank you for prompt reply. I would like to suggest that sometimes you don't have to make translation elegant like a novel in combat text. (In story is fine to use btw)\n\nFor example, the latest patch changed character role from simple to understand word into something that too complicated than is necessary\n\nAttacker > Assault\nDefender > Warden\nAssist > Chorus", "timestamp": "2025-04-28T18:11:29.753000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["633215996508766229"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1366466722940326030", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1366461968638017547", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "Can we rollback the translations?", "forum_channel_id": "1180845276823564288", "thread_tags": ["1361168939622727801"]}
